# Project Tech Stack

## Frontend

- **Framework:** Next.js (latest stable version)
- **Language:** TypeScript
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS (latest stable version)
- **State Management:** React Context API
- **Forms:** React Hook Form
- **Validation:** Zod
- **UI Components:** Shadcn/UI

## Backend

- **Framework:** .NET 9 (Targeting latest stable version)
- **Language:** C# 12
- **Architecture:** Clean Architecture, Domain-Driven Design (DDD)
- **API Style:** RESTful Controller Endpoints
- **Data Access:** Entity Framework Core (EF Core)
- **Database:** PostgreSQL (Inferred from Npgsql package)
- **Object Mapping:** Manual Mappers
- **Identifiers:** ULIDs
- **HTTP Clients:** Refit with HttpClientFactory
- **CQRS/Mediator:** MediatR
- **Result Handling:** FluentResults
- **Authentication/Authorization:** Keycloak (via `Keycloak.Net.Core` and `Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authentication.JwtBearer`)
- **API Versioning:** `Asp.Versioning.Mvc`
- **API Documentation:** OpenAPI (Swagger via `Swashbuckle.AspNetCore`)
- **Configuration:** `IOptions` pattern
- **Logging:** Structured Logging (Microsoft.Extensions.Logging)

## Common Backend Packages

- `Asp.Versioning.Mvc` / `Asp.Versioning.Mvc.ApiExplorer`
- `Keycloak.Net.Core`
- `Refit` / `Refit.HttpClientFactory`
